 .-------------------------------------------------------------.
| USAGE: SITE GIVE <username> <kbytes>[gGmM] <message>          |
|        (NOTE: The message part is optional)                   |
|                                                               |
| Example: SITE GIVE user 1000 Here's some credits for ya, pal! |
|          (This would give user 'user' 1 meg of your credits)  |
|          The g/m suffix is to specify gigabytes or megabytes  |
 `-------------------------------------------------------------'
